        Parameters:

                java.lang.String sourceFile,
                int line,
                int col,
                java.lang.String targetName,
                Type staticType,
                Expression... parameters)
        Builds the open call, happening at the given location in the program.
        Parameters:
        cfg - the cfg that this expression belongs to
        sourceFile - the source file where this expression happens. If unknown, use null
        line - the line number where this expression happens in the source file. If unknown, use -1
        col - the column where this expression happens in the source file. If unknown, use -1
        targetName - the name of the target of this open call
        parameters - the parameters of this call
        staticType - the static type of this call
